         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, 10/10/78 ¶ Dear Mr. Ramsay ¶  ¶ This letter reaches you from my sick bed, my assistant kindly writing it at my dictation. The Diatomaceae which you so kindly procured arrived safely during ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">78.10.10</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edward Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">ML MSS.562, Letters to E. P. Ramsay 1862-91, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS written by Georg Luehmann and edited and signed by M.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation: 'The plant was sent by Mr James Ramsay from "<seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Tindarie</hi>
                     </seg>" near Bourke, to his brother EPR — it will doubtless prove a very valuable plant as the sheep thrive on it — and it grows on all the dry land in the interior'. <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>See also ‘A new pasture shrub’,<seg style="font-style: italic; "> Riverine herald</seg> (Echuca, Vic), 2 November 1878, p. 2, for more details of James Ramsay’s account of the plant sent to his brother.</p>
               </note>Melbourne, 10/10/78</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Mr. Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This letter reaches you from my sick bed, my assistant kindly writing it at my dictation. The <name key="Diatomaceae">Diatomaceae</name> which you so kindly procured arrived safely during my absence. The bush sent by your brother from Cooper's Creek, so much liked by sheep, is <name key="Eremophila%20longifolia">Eremophila longifolia</name>. It has a very wide range over the inland regions of Australia reaching from Spencers Gulf to Shark Bay, also approaching the coast. Would it be troubling you too much kindly to tell me at what date the mission barque will leave Sydney. Pray present my salutation in return to Baron Miklucho Maclay<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nikolai Miklouho-Maclay?</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With kind regards</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Diatomaceae">Diatomaceae</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Eremophila%20longifolia">Eremophila longifolia</name>
            </p>
